name: Custom iPhone case for Michal
description:
- 3D full wrap-around design, the pattern goes all over the case
- Fits for all version of iPhone 4 / 4s and iPhone 5
- Made one at a time using our latest 3D full wrap-around technique
- Print directly on the case with vivid color and top quality
- 100% scratch proof and water proof
- Slim and light weight, won't destroy the beauty of your iPhone
- Easy to snap in and access to all ports, control and sensors
- Carefully packed and send with box and bubble envelop

▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼
This is a lovely handmade iPhone case which fits for both iPhone 4 and iPhone 4s.
